// DocumentEditor
// Split-pane editor for markdown documents.
// Left pane is a CodeMirrorWrapper; right pane is a MarkdownPreview with
// optional diff support. Supports annotations, version history, sync toggle,
// diff toggle, minimap, and clean export.

FUNCTION DocumentEditor(document, onContentChange, onSave, onCancel, ...) -> JSX  EXPORT
  CALLS: CodeMirrorWrapper (CodeMirrorWrapper), MarkdownPreview (MarkdownPreview)
  Renders a SplitPane with editor left and preview right.
  Optionally renders Minimap when enabled.
  Shows AnnotationToolbar when annotations are active.
  Keyboard shortcuts: Ctrl+S triggers handleSave; Escape triggers handleCancel
  if there are unsaved changes.
  Toolbar provides: sync scroll toggle, diff toggle, Export Clean button,
  HistoryModal trigger.

---

FUNCTION handleSave() -> void
  Calls onSave with current content.

---

FUNCTION handleCancel() -> void
  Only called when hasChanges. Calls onCancel to reset to saved state.
